posts.post_content:
Here’s a link to what I have, I’m only looking to trade for cards I need, I’m not selling.  If it’s not in the tradebait section, I’m probably not trading.  Thanks for looking, pm me here if you’re interested.  Unfortunately, if you email me and I don’t know you, well we know about scammers on the board.

[url]https://ed-s-cards.webnode.page/trade-bait/[/url]
T212s and T205s are all traded.
Made a few trades, still lots of good stuff left!

A nice assortment of T210s, some tough series 6 cards, a couple from other series.  Beaters to beauties, let’s make some trades.  Four T217 Mono’s, two are really nice, two are on the tougher side.  Great chance for a tough type card.  The T209s are gone, the T212s are gone, the T205s are gone.
